Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这做工真是渣\N{\fs38}T-t-t-this is just sloppy craftsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 Rick\N{\fs38}Hey, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看呀 今天天可真好呀 是吧\N{\fs38}Boy, sure is really especially beautiful out there today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 Morty\N{\fs38}oh, yes, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直好得不可思议 是吧\N{\fs38}I-it's almost unbelievable, Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs38}Yeah, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气格外清新\N{\fs38}There's something about the air
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳光分外明媚\N{\fs38}And just the way the sunshine is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 伙计 没错\N{\fs38}uh, sure, buddy. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 棒极了\N{\fs38}Sure. B-brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我简直都要信了\N{\fs38}Very convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么信了\N{\fs38}Wha convincing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 还能实时应答啊 真棒\N{\fs38}Oh. Responsive, too. In real time. I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}Uhh...okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去工作了\N{\fs38}I'm going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 早上好\N{\fs38}Morty, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:00:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 早上好\N{\fs38}Dad, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去工作了 再见\N{\fs38}I am going to work. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老妈怎么了\N{\fs38}what's with mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.21,0:01:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老妈怎么了\N{\fs38}oh, what's with mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说她举止很奇怪吗\N{\fs38}So, you're saying that she's acting weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得这么精细 小心点哟\N{\fs38}How sophisticated. Careful, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把中央处理器烧咯\N{\fs38}You're gonna burn out the cpu with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 Rick\N{\fs38}Okay, you know what, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天也很奇怪\N{\fs38}You'reacting weird, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你怎么说 所谓的"Morty"\N{\fs38}whatever, quote-unquote "Morty."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}all right, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那放学见了\N{\fs38}I'll see you after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 噢\N{\fs38}Ow! Oof! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs38}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事 我没事\N{\fs38}I'm all right. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来说说五乘以九等于多少\N{\fs38}All right, who can tell me what 5 x 9 is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38}Morty\NMorty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs38}uh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五乘以九等于多少\N{\fs38}What is 5 x 9?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.77,0:01:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等于\N{\fs38}umm...you know, it's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 至少四十吧\N{\fs38}Uhh...at least 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 完全正确\N{\fs38}Morty, that's exactly correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五乘以九等于至少四十\N{\fs38}5 x 9 is at least 40!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.97,0:01:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上这儿来\N{\fs38}Come up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真棒 Morty\N{\fs38}Whoo! Way to go, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同学们 这是我们最好的学生\N{\fs38}Everybody, this is the best student.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你来当老师\N{\fs38}I want you to be the teacher today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教教我们 Morty\N{\fs38}Teach us, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\fs38}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想让我教什么\N{\fs38}W-w-w-what do you want me to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么制造浓缩暗物质啊\N{\fs38}How do you make concentrated dark matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个好问题\N{\fs38}Oh, that's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:01:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浓缩什么\N{\fs38}concentrated huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浓缩暗物质\N{\fs38}Concentrated dark matter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加速级星际航行所需的燃料\N{\fs38}The fuel for accelerated space travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道要怎么制造吗\N{\fs38}Now, do you know how to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs38}umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊 Morty\N{\fs38}Come on, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的外公不是个科学家吗\N{\fs38}Isn't your grandpa, like, a Scientist?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 但是 他和我说\N{\fs38}oh, yeah, but, you know, he told me that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不可以随便告诉别人\N{\fs38}I shouldn't go around spouting off about,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的科学研究之类的\N{\fs38}you know, his science and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定看见过他制作浓缩暗物质很多次吧\N{\fs38}I bet you've seen him make concentrated dark matter a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你告诉我们\N{\fs38}You know, if you tell us,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就当你的女朋友\N{\fs38}I'll be your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs38}Uh, y-you will?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会难得啊 Morty\N{\fs38}Seems like a rare opportunity, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 快来\N{\fs38}Morty, u-uh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里有急事\N{\fs38}There's a family emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住\N{\fs38}Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他走了 我就挂了他这科\N{\fs38}If he leaves, I'm giving him an "F."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不在乎\N{\fs38}he doesn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 天\N{\fs38}aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 我必须得回去\N{\fs38}Rick, I have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我就要结婚了\N{\fs38}I think I was about to get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔\N{\fs38}Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起洗澡 Morty\N{\fs38}take a shower with me, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs38}what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 Morty\N{\fs38}listen to me, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把衣服脱了过来洗澡\N{\fs38}Get your clothes off and get in the shower right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我 Morty\N{\fs38}Y-y-y-you got to trust me, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs38}ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会挂科的 Rick\N{\fs38}I'm gonna get an "F" In class, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你没在上课\N{\fs38}Morty, that's not class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不是你的老师\N{\fs38}T-t-t-that wasn't your teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也不是你的学校\N{\fs38}This isn't your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界也不是我们的世界\N{\fs38}This entire world is not the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在一个外星飞船上的大型模拟舱里\N{\fs38}We're inside a huge simulation chamber on an alien spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs38}wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么\N{\fs38}W-what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是假的\N{\fs38}it's all fake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 全都是\N{\fs38}Morty, all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳米级机器渲染 搞出来的假玩意儿 Morty\N{\fs38}Nanobotic renderings, a bunch of crazy fake nonsense, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在淋浴间我才能跟你说\N{\fs38}I couldn't say so until we got in the shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里他们不会监视\N{\fs38}They won't monitor us in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监视我们吗 谁\N{\fs38}Monitor us?! W-who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙骗子Z星人 Morty\N{\fs38}Zigerion scammers, Morty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星系里最雄心勃勃却最失败的诈骗集团\N{\fs38}The galaxy's most ambitious, least successful con artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运的是\N{\fs38}You know, it's lucky for us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没法直视裸体\N{\fs38}They're also really uncomfortable with nudity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了 Rick\N{\fs38}Aw, come on, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果今天大家都不正常\N{\fs38}If everyone's just gonna be insane today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我要和Jessica一起发疯\N{\fs38}at least let me be insane with jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 Morty\N{\fs38}I can't let you do that, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我\N{\fs38}Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs38}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我\N{\fs38}You give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我 Rick\N{\fs38}G-g-give it! No, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啦 长官\N{\fs38}Oh, god, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还是裸着的\N{\fs38}They're still naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗷\N{\fs38}Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每隔五昆顿检查一次\N{\fs38}Well, check every five quintons
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他们不裸了再通知我\N{\fs38}And tell me when they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得该让Kevin来盯着 长官\N{\fs38}I think we should make kevin look, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 不\N{\fs38}What?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛这么说\N{\fs38}W-w-why would you even say that?
